      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s05_e007",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "正方形的定义：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s05_e008",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "> 有一组邻边相等且有一个角是直角的平行四边形叫作正方形。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 106,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s05_e009",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "两个条件缺一不可：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 204,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s05_e010",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ❌ 只有一组邻边相等（没有直角）：是菱形，不是正方形",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 252,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s05_e011",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ❌ 只有一个角是直角（没有邻边相等）：是矩形，不是正方形",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 346,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s05_e012",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ✅ 两个条件同时满足才是正方形",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 440,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
