          "id": "21.7_s09_e004",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "例1 在正方形 ABCD 中，点 E 在对角线 AC 上。求证：BE = DE。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 606,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s12",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s09_e005",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "分析：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s09_e006",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- 要证 BE = DE → 证 △ AEB  △ AED",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 102,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s09_e007",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- 三个条件： 1. AB = AD（正方形四条边相等） 2. ∠ BAC = ∠ DAC（正方形对角线平分对角） 3. AE = AE（公共边）",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 196,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 136,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s09_e008",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "（请动笔书写完整证明过程，限时2分钟）",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 340,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s13",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s10_e001",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "第9页：例1 · 标准证明",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 28,
          "bold": true,
          "color": "#12355b"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s10_e002",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "证明：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 106,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s10_e003",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∵ 四边形 ABCD 是正方形，",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 158,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s10_e004",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ AB = AD，∠ BAC = ∠ DAC。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 210,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s10_e005",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "又 ∵ AE = AE，",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 262,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s10_e006",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ △ AEB  △ AED（SAS）。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 314,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s10_e007",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ BE = DE。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 366,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s10_e008",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "关键：正方形对角线平分对角（∠ BAC = ∠ DAC = 45°）——这是从菱形继承来的性质。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 430,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s10_e009",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "变式追问：如果 E 在 AC 延长线上，BE 还等于 DE 吗？为什么？",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 528,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s14",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e001",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "第10页：例2 · 当正方形遇上等边三角形",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 28,
          "bold": true,
          "color": "#12355b"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e002",
          "type": "image",
          "src": "ed992442e34fce4803d61357ec05c367ba8edd6aa62585a3ebc1e4ed83c2f3cb.jpg",
          "x": 280,
          "y": 106,
          "width": 720,
          "height": 420
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e003",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "图21.7-2",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 542,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e004",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "例2 在正方形 ABCD 中，△ BCE 是等边三角形。求证：∠ EAD = ∠ EDA = 15°。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 606,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s15",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e005",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "分步引导：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e006",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "步骤  问题  依据",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 106,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 20,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#333333"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e007",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "①  △ BCE 是等边三角形 → BC = BE，∠ EBC = 60°  等边三角形性质",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 154,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 20,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#333333"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e008",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "②  ABCD 是正方形 → AB = BC，∠ ABC = 90°  正方形性质",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 248,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 20,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#333333"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e009",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "③  AB = BE（由①+②等量代换），∠ ABE = 90° - 60° = 30°  等量代换、角度差",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 342,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 20,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#333333"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e010",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "④  △ ABE 中，∠ BAE = 1/2(180° - 30°) = 75°  等腰三角形底角公式",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 436,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 20,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#333333"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e011",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "⑤  ∠ EAD = 90° - 75° = 15°，同理 ∠ EDA = 15°  角度差、对称性",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 530,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 20,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#333333"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s11_e012",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "（请跟随教师分步书写证明过程）",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 628,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s16",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e001",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "第11页：例2 · 完整证明",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 28,
          "bold": true,
          "color": "#12355b"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e002",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "证明：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 106,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e003",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∵ 四边形 ABCD 是正方形，",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 158,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e004",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ AB = BC，∠ ABC = ∠ BAD = 90°。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 210,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e005",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∵ △ BCE 是等边三角形，",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 308,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e006",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ BC = BE，∠ EBC = 60°。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 360,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e007",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ AB = BE，∠ ABE = 90° - 60° = 30°。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 412,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e008",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ ∠ BAE = ∠ BEA = 1/2 × (180° - 30°) = 75°。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 510,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e009",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ ∠ EAD = ∠ BAD - ∠ BAE = 90° - 75° = 15°。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 608,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s17",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e010",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "同理 ∠ EDA = 15°。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e011",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ ∠ EAD = ∠ EDA = 15°。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 106,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e012",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "回顾推理链：等边 BC 正方形 AB=BE 等腰 30° 底角 75° 90°-75° 15°",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 170,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s12_e013",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "追问：证完 ∠ EAD = ∠ EDA = 15° 后，你还能求出哪些角？",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 268,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s18",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e001",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "第12页：做一做 · 开放探究",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 28,
          "bold": true,
          "color": "#12355b"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e002",
          "type": "image",
          "src": "3f11b4c032459808de96a7786e56eb93191e351162613a598960cbc38b1e6292.jpg",
          "x": 280,
          "y": 106,
          "width": 720,
          "height": 420
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e003",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "图21.7-3",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 542,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s19",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e004",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "做一做 点 E、F、G 分别在正方形 ABCD 的边 AB、AD 和 CD 上，且 EF ⊥ FG，AF = DG。求证：EF = FG。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 136,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s20",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e005",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "（先独立思考2分钟，再小组交流）",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e006",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "一线三垂直模型：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 106,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e007",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "A、F、D三点共线（F在AD上），产生三个直角：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 158,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e008",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ∠ EAF = 90°（正方形角A）",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 206,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e009",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ∠ EFG = 90°（已知，EF ⊥ FG）",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 254,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e010",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "- ∠ FDG = 90°（正方形角D）",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 302,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e011",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "证明思路：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 354,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e012",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∵ A、F、D三点共线，",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 406,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e013",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ ∠ AFE + ∠ EFG + ∠ GFD = 180°（平角），",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 458,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e014",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "即 ∠ AFE + 90° + ∠ GFD = 180°，得 ∠ AFE = 90° - ∠ GFD。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 556,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s21",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e015",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "在 Rt△ DGF 中，∠ DGF = 90° - ∠ GFD。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e016",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ ∠ AFE = ∠ DGF。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 152,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e017",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "在 △ AEF 和 △ DGF 中：",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 204,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e018",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "cases ∠ EAF = ∠ FDG = 90° \\\\ AF = DG   (已知) \\\\ ∠ AFE = ∠ DGF   (已证) cases",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 256,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 136,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s13_e019",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "∴ △ AEF  △ DGF（ASA），∴ EF = FG。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 400,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s22",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s14_e001",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "第13页：练习 · 当堂检测",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 54,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 28,
          "bold": true,
          "color": "#12355b"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s14_e002",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "练习 如图，正方形 ABCD 的对角线 AC 为菱形 AEFC 的一边，求 ∠ FAB 的度数。",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 106,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 90,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s14_e003",
          "type": "image",
          "src": "bbd6716c273b3148cc4c4da248fb1d28a58c1c2bfa7b2270dd80f1073842d7dd.jpg",
          "x": 280,
          "y": 204,
          "width": 720,
          "height": 420
        },
        {
          "id": "21.7_s14_e004",
          "type": "text",
          "text": "（独立完成，限时3分钟）",
          "x": 70,
          "y": 652,
          "width": 1120,
          "height": 44,
          "fontSize": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#222222"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21.7_s23",
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "21.7_s14_e005",
          "type": "text",
